頭條。<br />\n<br />\n所有香港人嘅抗爭行為同埋共產黨政府既反抗行為， 到最終都係引導至代表香港管理人嘅政治符號爭奪戰， 亦可以話係主流思想嘅爭奪戰。<br />\n<br />\n換句話講， 只要啲鬼佬一諗到香港就會諗起呢面旗， 見到呢面旗就會諗起香港人， 我哋喺佢哋嘅心入面就已經係一個被默認嘅政體。 當呢啲條件已經達成， 我哋就已經完成香港爭奪戰嘅第一步， 之後就係點樣令國際承認呢個政權/思想體， 協助我哋全力抵抗國安法。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港終有一日成功獨立， 軍隊可以繼續沿用呢支旗， 但係喺建國時期我哋更需要嘅係其他唔同嘅、 更加有親和力同知性嘅元素， 我哋到時可以諗過第二樣嘢。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBgARtt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBgARtt.png&h=c10c5ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07urdGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07urdGP.jpg&h=a91c3fcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89b68aa48c1c78f6a8ab6d269670550741c82554","tid":2030441,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:08:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ddf910a91491fa7992d333350526910b7bfaf15","tid":2030441,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:27:58.000Z","msg":"有獅子山都唔好有星"},{"pid":"977df2b73ba25cbf585f37f10c24e725d99ddced","tid":2030441,"uid":218242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T21:40:41.000Z","msg":"民族自強 香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53556a0fba93dffb00b6db8b0d93ebbbad682714","tid":2030441,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T21:46:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edf7ec2dee568481209574fb3974bc69fc6f053e","tid":2030441,"uid":213607,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T22:04:10.000Z","msg":"唔好啦 真係好柒 用翻藍白啦好嗎 舊香港已死呀"},{"pid":"a7981e0ea874697f09a042c21feddc3305cb70b6","tid":2030441,"uid":346503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:25:20.000Z","msg":"睇到扯晒旗"},{"pid":"05eff8634d4c30827425ee5dc797dd021cd6d697","tid":2030441,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply